00:01:14.588 --> 00:01:21.213
have an equivalent fraction for 3/8. I can now rewrite the problem using my

00:01:21.225 --> 00:01:28.210
equivalent fractions. I have 14 over 24 plus 9 over 24. When I add fractions, I

00:01:28.222 --> 00:01:34.760
